### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/your-project-id/us-central1/api
@apiVersion = api
@assetId = replace_with_actual_asset_id

### Get All Assets
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Asset by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/{{assetId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Asset
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Asset",
  "assetType": "equipment",
  "purchaseDate": "2025-05-01T12:00:00.000Z",
  "purchasePrice": 1999.99,
  "status": "active",
  "description": "Test asset description",
  "location": "Main Office",
  "notes": "Test notes"
}

### Update Asset
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/assets/{{assetId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Asset Name",
  "status": "maintenance",
  "notes": "Updated test asset notes"
}

### Delete Asset
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/assets/{{assetId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Assets by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/type/equipment
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Assets by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/status/active
Content-Type: application/json